+- [ ] **Step 1: Update requirements.txt**
+
+```txt
+# backend/requirements.txt
+fastapi>=0.115.0
+uvicorn[standard]>=0.30.0
+sqlalchemy[asyncio]>=2.0.0
+aiosqlite>=0.20.0
